data.description: NEW PHOTOS! Located in Diamond Glen, the park-like gated 55+ community in the heart of Folsom, near historic Sutter Street!  Great location on a quiet street, near walking trail and Club House. The HOA maintains the front yard, home exterior sides and roof! This home is the largest floor plan with a covered front porch area, Two Primary Suites, a 3rd bedroom/Den and and Two full bathrooms.  Great room concept w/vaulted ceilings, and large windows, very light and bright! Updated kitchen w/stainless appliances, painted cabinets, and large walk-in pantry. Luxurious Vinyl Plank flooring and plantation shutters. You'll enjoy the private backyard patio with newer retractable awning.  Close to pool/spa, tennis/pickleball courts, trails, shopping, dining, medical, the American River Parkway, HWY 50 and so much more! This home is ready for immediately move in!
